No. —, original.

New Jersey v. City of New York. Motion submitted May 13, 1929. Decided May 20, 1929. Messrs. Duane E. Minard and Williams A. Stevens for complainant. Messrs. Arthur J. W. Hilley and J. Joseph Lilly for defendant. Per Curiam:

Motion for leave to file a bill of complaint herein is granted, and process is ordered to issue, returnable on Monday, May 27 next.
